OL,6,FSir Alan Bates told ITV News the prime
OL,7,Fminister has not responded to his
OL,8,Frequest to bring forward compensation
OL,9,Fpayments for wrongly convicted sub-
OL,10,Fpostmasters, as ITV News'
OL,11,FInvestigations Editor Daniel Hewitt
OL,12,Freports
OL,14,FSir Alan Bates has told ITV News that
OL,15,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer has
OL,16,Fignored two letters he has written to
OL,17,Fhim regarding ongoing delays to
OL,18,Fcompensation for sub-postmasters.
