OL,6,FThe Post Office campaigner first wrote
OL,7,Fto the prime minister on October 2,
OL,8,Fand again a few days ago, urging him
OL,9,Fto ensure victims receive full
OL,10,Ffinancial redress by March next year,
OL,11,Fbut Sir Alan has not received any
OL,12,Freply.
OL,14,F"I've had very little contact with the
OL,15,Fnew government," Sir Alan told ITV
OL,16,FNews.
