OL,6,FOn the Police investigation, Sir Alan
OL,7,Fsaid he's optimistic they are taking
OL,8,Fit seriously and will act.
OL,10,FThe criminal inquiry is being led by
OL,11,FCommander Stephen Clayman, Head of
OL,12,FCentral Specialist Crime at the
OL,13,FMetropolitan Police, and is assessing
OL,14,Fpotential offences of perjury and
OL,15,Fperverting the course of justice.
OL,17,FSince launching the investigation in
OL,18,FJanuary 2020, detectives have
OL,19,Finterviewed three people and made no
OL,20,Farrests.
