OL,6,F"They have put together a big team to
OL,7,Fwork on it," said Sir Alan.
OL,9,F"They did say... it could be a couple
OL,10,Fof years until they actually managed
OL,11,Fto move forward with any sort of
OL,12,Fcertainty on cases, but I do think
OL,13,Fthey recognise how serious all of this
OL,14,Fhas been, and I do think they are
OL,15,Factually going to act at the end of
OL,16,Fthe day.
OL,18,F"Well if they don't, we will."
