OL,6,F"I think that response was issued
OL,7,Fearlier today. On the substance of the
OL,8,Fissue, the government is committed to
OL,9,Fgetting redress to those affected as
OL,10,Fquickly as possible and is doing all
OL,11,Fit can to increase the pace of redress
OL,12,Facross all schemes."
OL,14,FThe spokesman added: "What we don't
